  <name>FE MEDIA CONVERTER</name>
  <summary>Professional video, audio and image conversion application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      FE MEDIA CONVERTER is a professional media conversion application that supports
      video, audio, and image formats. It provides advanced filtering options,
      GPU acceleration, and AI-powered enhancements for high-quality conversions.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Convert videos, audio files, and images to various formats</li>
      <li>Advanced video filters with automatic optimization</li>
      <li>Professional audio filters and equalizer</li>
      <li>Image enhancement and upscaling</li>
      <li>GPU acceleration support (NVIDIA, AMD, Intel)</li>
      <li>AI-powered video restoration (VRT)</li>
      <li>Batch conversion with queue management</li>
      <li>Custom resolution and quality settings</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
